trans-unit.source: A secure and interoperable binding that supports federated security.
trans-unit.target: En sikker og brukes sammen binding som støtter sammenslått sikkerhet.

trans-unit.source: Federation is the ability to share identities across multiple systems for authentication and authorization.
trans-unit.target: Sammenslåingen er muligheten til å dele identiteter på tvers av flere systemer for godkjenning og godkjenning.

trans-unit.source: These identities can refer to users or to machines.
trans-unit.target: Disse identiteter kan referere til brukere eller maskiner.

trans-unit.source: Federated HTTP supports SOAP security as well as mixed-mode security, but it does not support exclusively using transport security.
trans-unit.target: Samlet HTTP støtter SOAP sikkerhet, samt blandet modus sikkerhet, men støtter ikke bruk utelukkende av transportsikkerhet.

trans-unit.source: This binding provides [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] support for the WS-Federation protocol.
trans-unit.target: Denne bindingen gir [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] støtte for WS Federation-protokollen.

trans-unit.source: Services configured with this binding must use the HTTP transport.
trans-unit.target: Tjenester som er konfigurert med denne bindingen, må bruke HTTP-transport.

trans-unit.source: Bindings consist of a stack of binding elements.
trans-unit.target: Bindinger består av en bunke binding elementer.

trans-unit.source: The stack of binding elements in WSFederationHttpBinding is the same as that contained in <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding> when <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding.Security%2A> is set to the default value of <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpSecurityMode>.
trans-unit.target: Stakken for binding elementer i WSFederationHttpBinding er den samme som finnes i <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding>når <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding.Security%2A>er satt til standardverdien for <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpSecurityMode>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpSecurityMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding.Security%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding>

trans-unit.source: The WSFederationHttpBinding controls the details of the message security settings, the values of which are available from the instance of <xref:System.ServiceModel.FederatedMessageSecurityOverHttp> that is returned by the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpSecurity.Message%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: WSFederationHttpBinding kontrollerer detaljene for sikkerhetsinnstillingene meldingen, verdiene som er tilgjengelig fra forekomsten av <xref:System.ServiceModel.FederatedMessageSecurityOverHttp>som er returnert av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpSecurity.Message%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpSecurity.Message%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.FederatedMessageSecurityOverHttp>

trans-unit.source: The WSFederationHttpBinding also provides a <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpBinding.PrivacyNoticeAt%2A> property to set and retrieve the URI at which the privacy notice is located.
trans-unit.target: WSFederationHttpBinding gir deg også en <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpBinding.PrivacyNoticeAt%2A>egenskapen til å angi URIEN som personvernerklæringen er plassert.</xref:System.ServiceModel.WSFederationHttpBinding.PrivacyNoticeAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > When calling a [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service built with [!INCLUDE[netfx40_short](~/add/includes/netfx40-short-md.md)] from a WCF client application built with [!INCLUDE[netfx35_short](~/add/includes/netfx35-short-md.md)] or earlier, the configuration file generated by svcutil.exe or adding a service reference from [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] contains the `establishSecurityContext` attribute in the binding configuration.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når du kaller en [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjenesten som er bygget med [!INCLUDE[netfx40_short](~/add/includes/netfx40-short-md.md)] fra en WCF-klientprogrammet bygget med [!INCLUDE[netfx35_short](~/add/includes/netfx35-short-md.md)] eller tidligere, konfigurasjonsfilen genereres ved svcutil.exe eller legge til en referansen fra [!INCLUDE[vsprvs](~/add/includes/vsprvs-md.md)] inneholder den `establishSecurityContext` attributtet i bindingskonfigurasjonen av.

trans-unit.source: This attribute is not recognized by the [!INCLUDE[netfx35_short](~/add/includes/netfx35-short-md.md)] runtime and the application throws an <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationErrorsException> with the message "Unrecognized attribute establishSecurityContext ".
trans-unit.target: Dette attributtet gjenkjennes ikke av den [!INCLUDE[netfx35_short](~/add/includes/netfx35-short-md.md)] runtime og tjenesteprogrammet oppstår en <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationErrorsException>med meldingen "Ukjent attributt establishSecurityContext".</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationErrorsException>

trans-unit.source: To workaround this problem, remove the `establishSecurityContext` attribute from the binding configuration.
trans-unit.target: Å løse dette problemet ved å fjerne den `establishSecurityContext` attributtet fra bindingskonfigurasjonen.
